  We wanted a clear case so we could see the beautiful colors in the new iPhone 11‚Äôs. I‚Äôve always been an Otter box fan but I didn‚Äôt like the chunkiness of their clear case. Well I‚Äôm a professional phone dropper. If only someone would pay me for it I‚Äôd be rich. I drop it all the time on the ground in the car, in the kitchen, pretty much everywhere. The screen protector has yet to crack up and there‚Äôs enough of a lip around the edge Of both the front and the back that the camera is protected and the screen is protected. I‚Äôm really happy with this case.

This case also doesn‚Äôt have raised corners on the backside like some do, which is something I didn‚Äôt want. It comes with 4 pieces - The front bumper, the full body case, and two screen protectors. I didn‚Äôt use a protector because I have one coming in the mail, but I placed one on my screen to show you how well it fits. It‚Äôs designed for you to put on the case and then the protector, so you can accurately place the protector. It also isn‚Äôt too bulky, but still feels like it‚Äôs protecting my phone really well. I will definitely be using the vendor for all my phone protection needs. The value CANNOT be beat!
", '
  It‚Äôs hard to put into words how much I truly love this case. I have a horrible time finding a case that not only slides in and out of my back pocket without getting caught up, but isn‚Äôt so slim and slick that I‚Äôm constantly dropping it (as I do when there is no case on my phone, which is often, since I hate most of the cases I try). This case is perfect.It‚Äôs absolutely crystal clear and both the front ridged bumper piece and the slightly more flexible back cover piece are flawless and quite sturdy.I had no issues at all with installing the case and the screen protector went on gorgeously. For someone with massive OCD when it comes to alignment and imperfect areas/edges, this is huge. And it comes with 2! I‚Äôm able to type just fine with the screen protector on, which I can be a real snob over.I have a card holder adhered to the back of the case, which seems to be working super well.Overall, I‚Äôm crazy impressed. I‚Äôll only be back to review if somehow this god worthy case takes a crazy turn for the worst, which is highly unlikely.
', '

I have the white iPhone 11 and I‚Äôm not the best with applying screen protectors and I was definitely skeptical about the easiness of putting the 3 part case on it but it was extremely easy and both came on perfectly. Took me just a few minutes as well. I was afraid of breaking the front frame but reading the directions saying to remove it from bottom to top first AND watching the video helped a lot.
